pipiwharauroa
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(also called shining cuckoo, bronze-winged cuckoo) the smaller of the two migrant cuckoos that summer in New Zealand.
Origin:Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes:
